{"tid":1554153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［極度心寒］請舉報及廣傳藍絲令人髮指行徑！！！","createTime":"2019-09-09T00:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:24:40.000Z","uid":104980,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3be002ae246dd2523bd32d55cfc43f130858a380","tid":1554153,"uid":104980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QhOQ9p-chY&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_QhOQ9p-chY%26feature%3Dshare&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=f79e0c38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QhOQ9p-chY&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">你睇下 係我地連登圍爐取暖既同時 呢班垃圾藍絲同時都係度圍內傳緊d fake news</span><br />\n<br />\n目的都係想<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抹黑示威者</span> 講到佢地大奸大惡<br />\n<br />\n條片出左1日都冇 就10萬人睇左 有1萬個like 係咪痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間講到話何式凝提供大量少女比義士搞 呢d咁撚無聊既野都有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nShow幾張帶口罩既照出黎d人就信到十足 屌我分分鍾仲可以告鳩你<span style=\"color: red;\">發佈兒童色情物品</span>添<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">佢地形容示威者係蟑螂之餘 係性呢方面仲要渲染到佢地好隨便</span> 賤過地底泥<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>再係咁搞落去 唔駛黑警出手 呢班藍絲既暴力都會伴隨埋性 更加覺得女義士唔係人 可以隨便落手 仲可以有黑警包庇</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n每個人心中都有自己既正義 呢班垃圾無腦藍絲正因為覺得自己行徑係「<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亂世之中堅持一直以黎既正義同初心</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n片入面仲講到話要救d無辜少女 真係痴鳩線 無中生有之餘仲要煽動人地既同情心<br />\n<br />\n同我一齊舉報呢件社會垃圾！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位多d睇下對家講既野 叫醒更多既人 或者洗鳩佢地版"},{"pid"